name: Spring
description:
Spring is part of "kisetsu". 
This digital painting plays with perspectives and words.
 Spring is symbol of rebirth and renewal, blossoming and opening. 
The Origin. 
Spring is also a resilient object (or OBJKT ;-)), that can be pressed or pulled but returns to its former shape when released. 
Resilient is also someone with the capacity to recover quickly from difficulties. 
What I see is not what everyone sees, look inside yourself, find the meaning.
